{% set color_global_theme__base_class = 'cl-color-global-themes' %}

<div {{ bem('wrap', [], color_global_theme__base_class) }}>
  <div class="text-field" data-component-alignment="left" data-component-width="max">
    <div class="text-field__inner">
      <div class="text">
        <h1>Global Themes</h1> 
        <p>This page outlines all components which have dial/component theme options. Each component below is housed within global theme applications. Global themes define the color pallete from which each component dial/component theme gets its color assignments.</p>

        <p>As you scroll down the page, each <code>global theme</code> is presented in sections. The <code>controls</code> panel in storybook allow you to select which dial option to apply to each component within each global theme application. You can select a dial option for one or all components and scroll down to each global theme context to see how that dial is applied in each global theme instance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

